# Place your SSL certificate files here:
#   fullchain.pem  — full certificate chain (cert + intermediates)
#   privkey.pem    — private key
#
# Recommended: use Certbot / Let's Encrypt
#   certbot certonly --webroot -w /var/www/html -d yourdomain.com
#   Then copy/symlink the output here.
#
# ⚠️  NEVER commit actual certificate files to version control.
# Add nginx/ssl/*.pem to your .gitignore
